{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "02", "m": "06", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "20", "M": "40", "S": "57"}}, "news": [{"title": "Welspun One plans to lease over 10 million sq ft in next three years", "para": "Welspun One plans to lease over 10 million sq ft of warehousing and industrial real estate in the next three years, nearly doubling its current operational footprint. The company is expanding into adjacent segments like in-city distribution and retail, with key projects including a large FTWZ development at Nhava Sheva and logistics parks in Pune and Bengaluru.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/welspun-one-to-lease-over-10-million-sq-ft-of-warehousing-space-in-major-expansion/131467517?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-105440/131467517.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "NGT sets up panel to probe \u2018illegal brick kiln, clay mining in Balasore", "para": "The National Green Tribunal has ordered a joint investigation into allegations of illegal brick kiln operations and unauthorized brick clay mining in Balasore district. A multi-agency panel will verify the charges and recommend corrective measures. The tribunal directed the panel to submit its report within one month. Notices have been issued to state officials and private parties.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/ngt-sets-up-panel-to-probe-illegal-brick-kiln-clay-mining-in-balasore/131467178?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-52350/131467178.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}, {"title": "ED arrests Earth Infrastructures' promoters in \u20b92,004-crore buyer fraud case involving over 19,000 buyers", "para": "Four promoters of Earth Infrastructures Ltd. were arrested by the Enforcement Directorate in a Rs 2,00